Sam Tomkins has agreed to rejoin Wigan on a four-year contract from 2016 . 
  The England international has cut short his stay in the NRL with New Zealand Warriors after becoming homesick . 
  Tomkins rejected an offer from Warrington to return to the Super League . 
  The 26-year-old left Wigan at the end of the 2013 season . 
  The 2012 Super League Man of Steel will rejoin his home-town club . 
 